Package de.frag.umlplugin.actions

All base actions used in several different toolbars are contained in this package.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
AbstractZoomAction Abstract zoom action.
DirectPrintGraphAction Prints graph.
ExportGraphAction Exports graphs to files (to images for example).
FitContentAction Action for fitting view contents.
HelpAction Action for showing help.
PrintPreviewGraphAction Prints graph with preview.
SettingsAction Action for access to settings.
ZoomInAction Action for zooming into view.
ZoomOutAction Action for zooming out of view.
